Class MainPageController

java.lang.Object
com.example.rupizzeria.MainPageController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class MainPageController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This class serves as the controller for the main page of the RU Pizzeria application. It handles interactions with various UI elements and opens views for different pizza options, menu, current orders, and placed orders.
Author:
Nithya Konduru, Dhyanashri Raman
